examples: Blah ! Why can't I get this computer to work!

definitions.definition: Imitative of idle, meaningless talk; used sometimes in a slightly derogatory manner to mock or downplay another's words, or to show disinterest in a diatribe , rant , instructions, unsolicited advice, parenting, etc. Also used when recalling and retelling another's words, as a substitute for the portions of the speech deemed irrelevant.
examples: Yeah, yeah, blah blah blah , Mom, you said this all yesterday.
And then he was like, "Oh, my brother's an Internet millionaire, blah blah blah ." Like I care!
labels: often three times in succession: blah blah blah !
definitions.label_groups: When spoken repeatedly, often three times in succession: blah blah blah !
